A Seafood Restaurant Where
You'll Find A Friendly,
Family Oriented Atmosphere...
Fresh Catch Seafood Grill serves impeccably fresh, quality seafood complemented with a variety of signature entrees, fresh vegetables and homemade chowders. Local owners Eric & Jocelyn Olson and the entire crew are pleased to welcome you to our restaurant.

Fresh Florida Seafood and Signature Land-Lover Dishes
/$
$
Locally owned, serving fresh superior fish that arrives whole daily, then is fileted on premises by our chefs to ensure superior quality. Complemented with a variety of signature land lover steak and chicken entrees, fresh vegetables and homemade chowders.
​
Owner, Eric Olson, has been fishing all his life and we benefit from his resources & connections to get the very best Florida seafood! We feature a variety of grilled, broiled, steamed, blackened, and fried seafood. Steaks, pasta, chicken, raw bar, desserts, and creative entree salads, take out, a full liquor bar, wine list and 12 cold beers on tap.
